{"tid":1767763,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【呀金開台】唔想凍死就快啲入黎圍爐啦","createTime":"2019-12-03T14:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T16:05:57.000Z","uid":31494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7c11e85b12734106d56e248a2f8782f38dfd7742","tid":1767763,"uid":31494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T14:09:35.000Z","msg":"唔該乜撚野藍絲五毛 你地可以上一頁啦 (比你地支持而成功都唔風光得去邊)<br />\n啲留言又毫無價值 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位學生哥 上班族夜晚返到屋企<br />\n係電腦面前放鬆緊嘅同時入黎睇下小弟打機 入到黎留個言吹下水又得<br />\n有咩趣事或者遇到咩大問題都可以入黎傾下 你肯講我肯聽。<br />\n唔求做一個萬人訂閱嘅YouTuber . 但求每次開Live 都有十幾廿人支持已經好滿足 !<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U8OZGyH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU8OZGyH.jpg&h=a9943244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[YouTube]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCk0U90hLkSNNVzvtR0Jg-AQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCk0U90hLkSNNVzvtR0Jg-AQ&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=6c9315ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCk0U90hLkSNNVzvtR0Jg-AQ</a><br />\n[正常情況] 每晚都會開 LIVE 玩唔同嘅 GAME<br />\n<br />\nDiscord Group Link : <a href=\"https://discord.gg/C5azmrK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FC5azmrK&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=0777a0a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/C5azmrK</a><br />\n呢個群主要係聚集一班鐘意 [打機 / 鳩噏 / 聽歌 / 唱歌 / 鐘意識朋友嘅人]<br />\n規矩就唔定啦 , 唔影響到人就OK 。"},{"pid":"fe0673df6d53e6c85ee5024d6479f88ee415f7f8","tid":1767763,"uid":31494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T14:09:54.000Z","msg":"【開台啦】<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763f92e54ed7086deb083d3324c2ac9e9dbf1093","tid":1767763,"uid":31494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T14:23:36.000Z","msg":"【開台啦】<img src=\"/assets/fa